data.description: Secluded paradise! 4.7+/- acres covered in mature Oaks with lovely views! Great location in a quiet area of North Fork. This custom home features a formal entry with hardwood flooring opening to the formal living room with vaulted ceiling and fireplace. The beautiful hardwood flooring continues into the formal dining room featuring a trey ceiling. The family room is open to the kitchen with a wood stove and a slider to the back patio. A fully equipped kitchen with Adobe tile floors, tile counter tops, updated lighting and faucet is great for the family chef or baker. A large master suite has a sliding farm door to the bathroom and french doors to the patio area. The huge master bath has a double sink vanity, walk-in closet, soaking tub and separate shower. 2 guest bedrooms and a guest bath are just down the hallway. Nice patio area to enjoy barbecues, an attached 2 car finished garage and gravel drive are more features you won't want to miss.
